Comment: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:21.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}看着你的侧脸
Comment: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}所注视着的
Comment: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:28.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}是下个季节
Comment: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}我明白的
Comment: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:36.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}痛彻心扉
Comment: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:41.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}却反射似的故做笑容
Comment: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:48.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}暧昧的线条在摇动的缝隙中
Comment: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:54.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}用天真的小聪明  连结着梦境
Comment: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:55.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}
Comment: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:57.94,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}满是谎言 （别离开我）
Comment: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:00.99,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}遍体磷伤  （能不能留下）
Comment: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.76,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}只有纯度高过一切
Comment: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:10.00,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}看啊  多么地耀眼（我该说些什么）
Comment: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.14,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}泪水结成的钻石
Comment: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:17.86,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}一切的终结就要开始
Comment: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:24.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}这永远无法忘记的季节
